.SH NAME
drm_mode_create_scaling_mode_property \- create scaling mode property
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_mode_create_scaling_mode_property
.BI "(struct drm_device *dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
DRM device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Called by a driver the first time it's needed, must be attached to desired
connectors.

Atomic drivers should use \fBdrm_connector_attach_scaling_mode_property\fP
instead to correctly assign \fIdrm_connector_state.picture_aspect_ratio\fP
in the atomic state.
